2.4 USER CONSTRAINTS
•	Students must rank all subjects offered to their Program ID.
•	Preferences cannot be modified after the allocation engine is triggered.
•	After final allocation, no manual modifications are permitted.
•	Students can select only subjects mapped to their specific program.

2.5 ASSUMPTIONS AND DEPENDENCIES
•	Accurate CGPA data is available prior to allocation.
•	All students submit complete rankings.
•	Seat capacities are predefined by the administration.
•	System depends on server and database availability.

